{"tid":855560,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"「長文」阿媽話想要個孫","createTime":"2018-10-10T06:21:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-10T13:14:57.000Z","uid":195511,"like":2,"dislike":50,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ac55323fb514e7c57dd84f264ef8ef926562e9fe","tid":855560,"uid":195511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T06:21:20.000Z","msg":"阿媽今年都70有多<br />\n而我今年都只係得21<br />\n原本我應該係一個阿哥<br />\n但阿哥出生冇耐就大病支持唔住過咗生<br />\n阿媽就係因為咁好自責<br />\n有咗好多年抑鬱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n過咗好耐先冇問<br />\n再生多個 就係我<br />\n <br />\n去到依家佢身體開始好差<br />\n有好多身體退化嘅問題出現<br />\n但佢真係好想係有生之年可以抱下孫咁<br />\n但係我仲讀緊書<br />\n而且女朋友都淨係得19歲<br />\n咁我都唔知係咪真係可以同佢過一生<br />\n所以我冇理由因為阿媽想抱孫而害咗一個咁後生嘅好女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我完全唔知點算好<br />\n又有唔想令到阿媽帶住遺憾咁走<br />\n又唔想害咗女朋友<br />\n我可以點...<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以最後我做咗一個好錯嘅決定..<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我喺自己打飛機就射嗰陣<br />\n射咗去阿媽隻眼度<br />\n俾佢睇下佢嘅乖孫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"674284fef4491189e518e35b0a3b99a38ee331a2","tid":855560,"uid":196077,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T06:37:16.000Z","msg":"直接同你老母做愛<br />\n孫又得仔又得 得撚咗"},{"pid":"96b077f03885c5922e12a98142a32b2edc021183","tid":855560,"uid":145194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T06:39:41.000Z","msg":"遲d會唔會有分報紙會寫「痴線兒子對母自慰，母心臟病發亡」"},{"pid":"b0b5e0cfc08dea9cfa7f5a3ea4be088112b95623","tid":855560,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T06:39:41.000Z","msg":"養寵物"},{"pid":"2de7133af11f5c1cdbb806c8cb11c25454a5efa7","tid":855560,"uid":195511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"674284fef4491189e518e35b0a3b99a38ee331a2","tid":855560,"uid":196077,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTi